title: Week Two Recap
itunes:title: Week Two Recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Nick Shook & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the games from week two of the regular season. Then the heroes break down the Sunday Night Football game where the Falcons didn’t seem to have any Super Bowl hangover.
